<p>How about doctors just grow a pair, assert their medical authority &amp; say something like &#8220;I am the doctor, I dont think you need (insert drug of choice)&#8230;. of course you can always get a second opinion.&#8221;</p>
<p></p>
<p>Its bad enought that I have to blow money/time on a 30 minute wait &amp; then a 5 minute &#8220;look-see&#8221; session with a doctor but to waste even MORE money on medicine that has no medicinal effect?</p>
		</div><!-- end .comment-content -->

		<div class="reply">
					</div>

		</li>

